    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready to roll at a budget-friendly price! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably, gets you where you need to go, and serves as a solid everyday driver. You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections that come with its age, but mechanically it holds its own for daily commuting and errands. If you're looking for dependable transportation without the premium price tag, this is a smart, practical pick!",
