    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Project car opportunity \u2014 priced to reflect its current condition! This vehicle is in poor condition and needs significant work, so we're being upfront about that from the start. It has visible body damage, wear throughout the interior, and mechanical issues that will require attention before it's road-ready. That said, it could be a great candidate for a hands-on DIY enthusiast, a parts donor, or someone with the skills to bring it back to life. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just an honest deal at an honest price!",
      "price": 5500.0,
