      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront about what that means before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 the paint is faded, scratched, and has areas of visible rust or corrosion that will require attention. Body panels may have dents or damage that goes beyond typical cosmetic blemishes. The interior is worn throughout, with tears, staining, or damage to the upholstery and trim. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require repairs to run reliably \u2014 it is not in road-ready shape without some investment. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs parts. We are pricing it accordingly and are transparent that this is a fixer-upper, not a daily driver in its current state.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition \u2014 it is priced accordingly and best suited for buyers who are mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or need basic transportation on a tight budget. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable scratches, dents, and paint fading or chipping in multiple areas. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn upholstery, cracked or damaged trim pieces, and general signs of age and neglect. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention and repair before it can be considered fully reliable \u2014 buyers should budget for additional work beyond the purchase price. There are no major hidden surprises here; what you see is what you get. This is an honest, straightforward listing for a vehicle that needs work, priced to reflect that reality.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
