      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 the highest designation we use, and one we apply only when a car truly earns it. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint is deep, rich, and free of scratches, chips, swirl marks, or any blemishes whatsoever. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, all trim pieces are intact and perfectly fitted, and the glass is crystal clear with no chips or cracks. The interior matches the exterior in every way \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, fading, or staining, all surfaces are pristine, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as it did from the factory. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, and the mechanical components are in excellent working order with no known issues. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has clearly been kept with exceptional care, and a buyer can expect to step in and enjoy a driving experience that feels as close to new as the used market allows.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
